Title: Write a short text adventure.
Description: Write possible actions in a text adventure.
Input.context: Long ago the bombs fell and the world ended. You are one of the few who is still alive. You are trying to survive by scavenging among the ruins of what is left behind.
Input.story_block_1: You search the gas station for food, but find nothing you can eat.
Input.story_block_2: You search the cars for food, you search three without success, but in the glove compartment of the fourth you find a box of crackers.
Answer.result: They remind you of when you needed to eat a bland diet after your operation. You pat yourself on where you remember the incision was made. The scar healed long ago, but the brain remembers. The crackers weren't very nutritious, but some fuel in the tank is better than none.

Input.previous_action_1: go inside the store and see if there are any supplies.
Input.story_block_2: It looks like the store has been ransacked and all the shelves are empty. You manage to find a package of granola bars and a flashlight behind the counter.
